            <title>[LU-14473] Verify RUNAS and RUNAS_ID separately from filesystem operation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14473</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Before running tests, the test framework executes&#160;check_runas_id_ret() to validate the configured RUNAS_ID.&#160; It tests this by attempting to touch a file.&#160; If the test fails, it&apos;s unclear whether the problem was with the runas utility, the configured ID, or the file system.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
